preference.name: TCAAE121_auxfiles_wdp
preference.preference_description: Through this option it is possible to specify the list of auxiliary file types to be created in Teamcenter together with the related AutoCAD Electrical project files. For each value specified in the list a dataset of the given type will be created/updated under the same item revision of the drawing being saved. Possible values: dwf dwfx pdf Values are considered as case-insensitive.
